description:
Any empty character slots on the team will 
be filled with Saibaimen during battle. 

{size : 24}{color : #FFFF00}{outline : #FF0000, 2}Copying Popular Teams{outline}{color}{size}

Stages in Quest each have three of the following 
four difficulties: 
- {color: #3366FF}NORMAL{color} 
- {color: #FF9900}HARD{color} 
- {color: #FF0000}Z-HARD{color} 
- {color: #9966FF}SUPER{color}

You can quit during a Quest (including map and battle) by going 
to "MENU" on the bottom right side of your screen and selecting 
{color: #FFFF00}"Abandon Quest."{color}

Each character has a Type. Below is the type compatibility chart:

·{color: #FF3333}STR (Red){color}: Strong against{color: #FFCC00} PHY (Orange){color}, 
  weak against {color: #66CCCC}AGL (Blue){color}
·{color: #66CCCC}AGL (Blue){color}: Strong against{color: #FF3333} STR (Red){color}, 
  weak against {color: #00CC00}TEQ (Green){color}
·{color: #00CC00}TEQ (Green){color}: Strong against{color: #66CCCC} AGL (Blue){color}, 
  weak against {color: #CC66FF}INT (Purple){color}
·{color: #CC66FF}INT (Purple){color}: Strong against{color: #00CC00} TEQ (Green){color}, 
  weak against {color: #FFCC00}PHY (Orange){color}
·{color: #FFCC00}PHY (Orange){color}: Strong against{color: #CC66FF} INT (Purple){color}, 
  weak against {color: #FF3333}STR (Red){color}

When you're up against a weaker Type, you'll do more damage, 
but when you're up against a stronger Type, the enemy will 
guard against your attack and you'll do less damage.

When the enemy is the first to attack, they will attack the 
character on the far left. In all other cases, enemies will target 
the {color: #FFFF00}"character who attacked just before them."{color}

{center: begin}Daily Missions{center} 
{center: begin}Normal Missions{center} 
{center: begin}Event Missions{center} 
{center: begin}Trial Missions{center} 
{center: begin}Portal of Memories{center} 

Missions are divided into the 5 types shown above. 

"Event Missions" also include time-limited missions related 
to events. You can claim the rewards of completed missions at 
any time, except for Daily Missions. Please note you will not 
be able to claim the Daily Mission rewards if you do not 
claim them before the daily update of the missions.

If a mission is completed, it will be marked with {color: #FFFF00}"CLEARED!"{color} 
on the mission list, and its frame will become yellow. 
You can tap on it to claim the rewards.

{color : #FFFF00}Baba's Shop{color} is a place where you can acquire various items by 
using your Trade Points, Zeni and Treasure.  

{size:25}{color : #FFFF00}▼Trade Points{color}{size}

{color : #FFFF00}Slightly raises the power of a Super Attack.{color} 
Any additional effects of the Super Attack will not change. 
The effect increases along with the skill level.

